channel.title: PandaPwn [New Coder]
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2ur00tc.png[/img] Welcome to the official development page of my first project (I am also known as "Zap"). Here I will be basically documenting my progress thought the development of the project, as well as posting things I need to fix and what ever I feel is necessary. The server base for my project is Delta.
[size=10pt]Stage:[/size] Working on skilling area. [size=10pt]To-do list[/size] Make Web Client Set up forums/website [25%] Add more items to shop inventory [75%] Add training area [25%] Add skilling area [50%] Add bosses (kbd,kqueen,gwd etc.) Finish Client (downloadable) [75%] Work on the economy Add training area [25%] [size=18pt]Pictures comming soon (only basics are done)[/size]
Project started on: February 17th, 2011
